[src:apache-flink/data-stream] Typically, the transmitted symbols are grouped into a series of packets.
[src:apache-flink/data-stream] Most data transmitted over the Internet is transmitted as a data stream.
[src:apache-flink/data-stream] Using a mobile phone to have a conversation transmits the sound as a data stream.
